[API] Deleting a token

You can delete a security token before it expires.

HTTP request syntax (URI) 

DELETE https://ipAddress:port/v1/security/tokens

Request structure

Not applicable.

Response structure

Not applicable.

Return codes

Status code

HTTP name

Description

200 OK Success
204 No content The request was successful, but if the response to be returned does not exist, return this code instead of 200.
401 Unauthorized The operation is not authorized.
403 Forbidden The server failed to authenticate the request.
